title: [Ta'Illistim, Fraendel Court]
description: The entire southeast corner of the Court is occupied by a large stone structure featuring an intricately worked iron door that contains a remarkably large bolt.  The door is flanked on either side by capable looking guardsmen who scan the crowd with a steady gaze.
